{"payload": {"model": "glm-4-flash-250414", "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "你是少样本时序分类专家。给你 K=6 个有标签的训练样本和 1 个 query 序列，请输出 query 的 class。\n\n候选 class: [1, 2]\n\n【训练样本】\n  [0] label=1: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['0.87', '0.92', '0.96', '0.94', '0.81', '0.66'], last=['0.36', '0.43', '0.59', '0.61', '0.68', '0.80']\n  [1] label=1: mean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['0.97', '1.11', '1.18', '1.16', '1.03', '0.91'], last=['0.19', '0.32', '0.45', '0.58', '0.71', '0.84']\n  [2] label=1: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['0.63', '0.66', '0.60', '0.55', '0.55', '0.44'], last=['0.16', '0.25', '0.34', '0.42', '0.52', '0.57']\n  [3] label=2: mean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['0.13', '0.12', '0.05', '-0.03', '-0.07', '-0.18'], last=['-0.35', '-0.27', '-0.20', '-0.09', '0.02', '0.10']\n  [4] label=2: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['2.14', '2.15', '2.04', '1.91', '1.75', '1.59'], last=['1.30', '1.43', '1.60', '1.72', '1.89', '2.05']\n  [5] label=2: mean=0.000, std=0.999, first=['1.40', '1.37', '1.25', '1.09', '0.93', '0.81'], last=['0.63', '0.80', '0.92', '1.04', '1.20', '1.32']\n\n【Query 序列】\nmean=-0.000, std=0.999, first=['0.95', '0.98', '0.92', '0.86', '0.75', '0.65'], last=['0.34', '0.45', '0.57', '0.66', '0.74', '0.86']\n\n输出 JSON（仅 JSON）：\n{\n  \"class\": <one of [1, 2]>,\n  \"confidence\": <0-1 float>,\n  \"reason\": \"<1 句话>\"\n}\n"}], "temperature": 0.1, "max_tokens": 1024}, "content": "```json\n{\n  \"class\": 1,\n  \"confidence\": 0.95,\n  \"reason\": \"The query sequence's mean and standard deviation are similar to those of the labeled training samples with label 1, and its first and last values are also closer to those of label 1 samples.\"\n}\n```"}